Make Total be 0

Repeat for Number in Range from 1 to 5
  If Number is 4
    Skip
  Change Total to Total plus Number

Expect Total is 11

Make Names be List with "Ada" and "Grace"
Make Maybe First be Item 0 of Names as Maybe String

Match Maybe First
  When Some First
    Expect First is "Ada"
  When nothing
    Expect false is true
